# BV Studios Website Project Structure

## Core Architecture
This is a Next.js 15.4.5 project using the App Router with Turbopack optimization. The main entry point is [app/layout.js](mdc:app/layout.js) which provides the root layout.

## Directory Structure

### App Router Pages
- [app/page.js](mdc:app/page.js) - Homepage with hero section
- [app/dashboard/page.js](mdc:app/dashboard/page.js) - User dashboard with file management
- [app/dashboard/project/[id]/page.js](mdc:app/dashboard/project/[id]/page.js) - Dynamic project pages
- [app/admin/dashboard/page.js](mdc:app/admin/dashboard/page.js) - Admin interface (1,678 lines)
- [app/admin/test-buttons/page.js](mdc:app/admin/test-buttons/page.js) - Admin testing page

### Components Organization
- [components/Navigation.js](mdc:components/Navigation.js) - Main navigation (optimized)
- [components/portfolio/PortfolioItem.js](mdc:components/portfolio/PortfolioItem.js) - Individual portfolio items
- [components/portfolio/VideoModal.js](mdc:components/portfolio/VideoModal.js) - Video modal component
- [components/navigation/AuthButton.js](mdc:components/navigation/AuthButton.js) - Authentication button
- [components/navigation/MobileMenu.js](mdc:components/navigation/MobileMenu.js) - Mobile menu
- [components/admin/Overview.js](mdc:components/admin/Overview.js) - Admin dashboard overview
- [components/admin/UsersManagement.js](mdc:components/admin/UsersManagement.js) - User management interface
- [components/contact/ContactFormLazy.js](mdc:components/contact/ContactFormLazy.js) - Optimized contact form

### API Routes
- [pages/api/files.js](mdc:pages/api/files.js) - File management API (optimized with caching)
- [pages/api/webhooks/stripe.js](mdc:pages/api/webhooks/stripe.js) - Stripe webhook handler (456 lines)
- [pages/api/auth/[...nextauth].js](mdc:pages/api/auth/[...nextauth].js) - NextAuth.js configuration

### Configuration Files
- [package.json](mdc:package.json) - Dependencies and scripts (Turbopack enabled)
- [next.config.js](mdc:next.config.js) - Next.js configuration
- [tailwind.config.js](mdc:tailwind.config.js) - Tailwind CSS configuration
- [prisma/schema.prisma](mdc:prisma/schema.prisma) - Database schema

## Key Technologies
- Next.js 15.4.5 with App Router
- Turbopack for development
- NextAuth.js for authentication
- Prisma for database
- Tailwind CSS for styling
- Framer Motion for animations
- Stripe for payments
